Class ConfirmationScreenController

  • java.lang.Object
    • common.controllers.AbstractScreen
      • clientSide.gui.ConfirmationScreenController
  • public class ConfirmationScreenController
extends AbstractScreen
    The ConfirmationScreenController is called after a booking if successfully proccessed, showing a confirmation (invoice) to the user.
